---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Services from '../components/Services.astro';
import Portfolio from '../components/Portfolio.astro';
import Testimonials from '../components/Testimonials.astro';
import Contact from '../components/Contact.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<Header />
<main class="space-y-20">
  
    <section class="bg-white py-20 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-32 relative">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <!-- Texte -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 leading-tight">
        Festival<br />
        <span class="text-green-600">Âge de Bière</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 font-medium">Aftermovie immersif</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Visuel vidéo -->
    <div class="relative flex justify-center">
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl max-w-md w-full border-4 border-black">
        <a href="/agedebiere-aftermovie.mp4" target="_blank">
          <div class="relative">
            <img src="/7.png" alt="Aftermovie Âge de Bière" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-80 rounded-full p-4 hover:scale-105 transition">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Points décoratifs -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0">
    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-10 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-10 w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-2 left-1/3 w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-20 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-32 relative">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
    <!-- Texte -->
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Contexte -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Contexte</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          À l'occasion du Festival Âge de Bière à La Chapelle-sous-Chaux, j'ai réalisé avec trois collègues un aftermovie d'environ 1 minute 30. L'objectif : capturer l'essence de l'événement, de la mise en place à l'ambiance festive, en valorisant les artisans, les brasseurs et les moments forts.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Intentions -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Intentions de réalisation</h3>
        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4">
          <li>Créer une narration visuelle fluide et dynamique</li>
          <li>Mettre en valeur les intervenants et l'ambiance artisanale</li>
          <li>Rendre l'expérience sensorielle : musique, lumière, convivialité</li>
          <li>Proposer un rythme court mais immersif (1'30)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Retour -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Retour d'expérience</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Ce projet m'a permis de travailler sur un format court mais dense, en gérant la captation terrain, le storytelling visuel et le montage. Une belle occasion de valoriser un événement local et d'améliorer encore mes compétences en narration visuelle.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Visuels -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
        <img src="/8.jpg" alt="Captation terrain Âge de Bière" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
        <img src="/9.jpg" alt="Setup vidéo Âge de Bière" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Points décoratifs -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0">
    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-10 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-10 w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-2 left-1/3 w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-20 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-32 relative">
  <!-- Titre -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">L’Aftermovie</h2>

  <!-- Vidéo -->
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-black relative">
    <a href="/agedebiere-aftermovie.mp4" target="_blank">
      <div class="relative">
        <img src="/9.jpg" alt="Aftermovie Festival Âge de Bière" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-80 rounded-full p-4 hover:scale-105 transition">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Points décoratifs -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0">
    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-10 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-10 w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-2 left-1/3 w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
  </div>
</section>







  <Contact />
</main>
<Footer />

